No. No. But to be proper and - correct and to - learn manners and - not to be crossing your hands over here or there on the table to - just - mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 If you wanted something that was on the table then how did you get it, did you ask for it?
