Oh - oh yes, we would have to - treat them properly and not allow them to do anything out of the way and - oh they were terrible for the sugar as there was no sweets on the isl
and. Sugar wouldn't last long you know in the house and - well that was a great time. They would get the smack when we would tell mother when she would come home but they'd carry on.
