No, but my mother used to take them on her lap, and put a cloth under this and tie it at the back, and there was the spoon. And then - from - from the sp
oon and the pouch and the - the - the milk bottle, they would get - the cup and drops of tea, and then a wee biscuit or anything dipped in the tea. Mm hm. Oh they were great you know.
