ds, like that. Aye, we used to be so pleased when we would get a beads, you know, these cheap beads with the - blue and - pink and uh huh, the women used to take that from the fishing - east coast. Fraserburgh. Peterhead and Aberd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033309\charrsid2102334 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 en. I would only cost a penny or tuppe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15033309\charrsid2102334 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 ce, but oh we were in our glory with the beads. Mm hm.
