No. No. No, they didn't play them. But - the men - in the wintertime when not at the fishing, over here in Barra, they used to gather in the wintertime and in one house, a ceidl house, and it was all stories of by gone days. Mm hm. Of the chie
fs and of the lords and of the landladies and of the - that kind of - uh huh.
