I
 have in mind, and will ever 'til the day I die that I read, it had such a great of meaning, the stories in glowing memories of the highland clearance. The Highland and Island clearance. It had such a great - to - to read - that they were tied, their hand
s and feet - them that weren't go - willing to go.
