\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10050444 KG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Yes, yes, yes. Fully depending that they would - he would - that he would do something and stand by them for the Western Isles. Mm hm.

