p another mother that hadn't a - a daughter that would look after her baby. That was it dear how it was going, nearly in every house helping. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 So that woman could go to the fishing?
