d stay a night, in that place, they'll go - when the - when the sound is dry they'll go over and graze. But whenever dusk comes they'll make for the - you know, come across from it, just like that island there, and - if the tide happens to come in and the
y
're grazing you know, they'll go and swim across, rather than to spend the night on the island. Mm hm. It's strange. There is strange things you know. Really and truly do you know it's just lately that I heard of places that - that was haunted. That kind 
