Oh no, no. No dear, there's not such a thing, no, no, dear, no, no. But - down in the old - in the houses and castles in Scotland. Well surely dear you've read about it often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 But that was interesting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10050444 KG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Wasn't it, about that woman that -
