\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10050444 KG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Not at first - until we were able to use it you know what - up in years, ten or twelve, could use it but}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
