, and the son was a shoemaker too, his father had had taught him you know, and - it was too much need you know for me to stay. They would take a - in - a woman to do the washing. Because that was all, just - there was nothing else but that and I would nee
d
 to take the for the fishing season, help the home - eight shillings wasn't much of a help then anyway you know. Mm hm. Well - for engaging - to engage at the fishing season for the summer season - two pound each month engagement money. And - what you wou
