pence a barrel for every barrel that we would fill to be shared between three, so if we would fill twenty barrels it would be something. Eight}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7808721\charrsid2102334  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 pence a barrel. Uh huh, that's it.
