 first place you were in, you'd get your - a r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7808721\charrsid2102334 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 ver - a good reverence \{BLANK\}
 And the next place and the next place and the next place, well - the people that you - that we were - we were with last year, they would want us back as soon as they would get to know that we arrive - arrived. Would like to come back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 So you went back to the same people again?
