\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Three pounds a week was good money for a woman then?
