would have a - lawyer, Mr Ambrose or Mr so and so, this and that and after she would be - be - have - an interview with her lawyers she used to take me with her to Cranstons tea rooms in Sauchiehall Street, that's a big place in Sauchiehall Street, I thin
k
 it remains, straight out of Glasgow town, she used to take me to Cranstons tea rooms with her and seemingly lady - there would be some ladies that she knew there too the same evenings, and - who used to pal with me but the maids - and they would say to m
e - you know - I - she - she - really as regards, you know - she was a good sight and I knew it and -
