 then the money got such a grip of her, and - she said to me once, Kate, she said, if you will stay with me you won't regret it. Well - I didn't say nothing to her but I - I just listened to her, to stay with her when I had to buy my own - most of my - my
 
wage was going out in food, but the lady next door in the next villa said to me, look here, she says, you go to the grocers, you go to the butcher and you go to the fishmonger, she says, buy anything that the house needs and yourself, and put the bill in 
to the lawyer. And you're Ok. That's her style, she said, and she was the same with every other maid. Just the same with any of the other maid. But -
