. Then - I being married you know and old fashioned in my ways, was quite all right with them. And I used to come into Oban on my day off, and help - go to McDougalls - go to McDougalls - con - contractors, Oban, and - it - when he would - when I would ge
t his letter telling me that - he would - that he was short of so many buttons, so many boards, I would come on my day off into Oban and go to McDougalls, they were awful nice to me too the McDougalls, and - so }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
