\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 The first was twins?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10050444 KG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Not - no dear. But the last kick-off was the twins. Double. Mm hm. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Is it your son Finlay that you're hoping to see in July?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10050444 KG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Yes. Yes and I'll tell you about that Finlay. Oh Finlay was very very intelligent, and he was very brainy. Some
thing like his Uncle John as regards music and - mechanic and all that, yes, and - I'll tell you one - blessing about Finlay. He was twenty-one years of age - when his father died, but of course he wasn't at home when his father died, he was away over on 
t
he other side of the world in America. He never answered his father back. Never, never, never gave his father an answer back. No. They were a good - they were good to me. They were good to me to tell you dear the truth, as good as a family ever was to a m
o
ther, and I was just putting that money back, saving their money for them. And when they got married, Finlay the first, three shares of their money was their own earnings, their mother was saving for them, they were sending me half - half pay every month.
 
I made two shares of it. His own share for me, then Roddy got married, the same shares to Roddy, but I was paying seven pound a week for he was in the sea school, he's an officer. A lieutenant or something, an officer. And - he got - and then So - I'm qui
te all right. I'm quite comfortable with my children and my health. I'm quite happy. Quite happy. Quite comfortable dear, I don't want working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 You have good health do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10050444 KG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Blessed with good health. Oh that's all I'm praying for and my memory and
 to keep my seven senses, that's all. Oh aye, and the - the best gift of all, the best gift of all for anybody is their - you know, their - their - your health of mind. Peace of mind, yes, uh huh. Major Bennet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 That was all on the mainland, your jobs in service?
