All on the mainland dear. Yes. I must - had to - run at the door - to learn from a beggar to a king. Go through the move like that. We had to. Mm hm. So it was a good job. Learn to put your hand to anything. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4786465 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4289636\charrsid2102334 Was that during the first world war you were in service?
